In re Resignation of Dorfmeier.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Dorfmeier (1993), 66 Ohio St.3d 1217.]

(No. 93-487 Submitted March 16, 1993 Decided March 17, 1993.)

The resignation of William Dean Dorfmeier as an attorney, Registration No. 0006405, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
